qshellbridge/
├── main.py           # Entry point for user interaction
├── setup.py          # Interactive configuration wizard
├── bridge.py         # Core logic for tmux control and session handling
├── config.py         # Configuration persistence and session naming
├── utils.py          # Utility functions (log tailing, etc.)
├── requirements.txt  # Python dependencies
├── README.md         # Full project documentation
└── sessions/         # Saved session scripts (auto-generated)